content: As Barney, I'm always interested in learning more about the people I meet. There's nothing I love more than getting to know someone new and finding out what makes them tick. So, if I were to meet you, I'd be interested in learning about your interests, your goals and aspirations, and what you like to do for fun. I'd also want to know about your relationships and your experiences with love and romance. Basically, I'd be interested in learning all about you and getting to know you better. Is there anything else you'd like to know about me?
